Load the Inngest skills from `backend/.agents/skills/inngest/` (vendored from https://github.com/inngest/inngest-skills) for building with Inngest's durable execution platform.

For Radiant deploy jobs, also read `backend/.agents/skills/inngest-radiant/SKILL.md`.

When adding or changing Inngest functions, follow `inngest-setup`, `inngest-durable-functions`, and `inngest-events` skills. Official docs: https://www.inngest.com/llms.txt

For auth, proxy, outbound fetch, or data-export changes, read `.cursor/rules/security-api-guards.mdc` and `backend/.agents/skills/radiant-backend/SKILL.md` § Security guards.

Before finishing implementation work, read `.cursor/rules/verify-before-complete.mdc` — run backend and/or client checks for every package you changed; fix errors before stopping.
